      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, maintained to a high standard of mechanical and aesthetic integrity. This unit offers a premier balance of performance and long-term value, having undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure continued reliability. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a documented service history, this vehicle represents a sophisticated choice for the discerning driver who prioritizes quality and proven engineering. We invite you to experience the refined road manners and enduring appeal of this exceptional model.",
