    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS. This example retains its linear power delivery to an 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded polyurethane bushings to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment, ensuring the valvetrain is within factory tolerances. While the aesthetics show minor wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are exceptional.",
